  <title>Project Properties</title>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1">Project Properties</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">There are several ways that you can set project properties in Visual Studio:</para>
    <list id="2" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="Normal">There is a &lt;Myprojectname&gt; Properties menu option in the Project Menu</li>
      <li styleclass="Normal">There is a context menu option &quot;Properties&quot; on the project icons in the Solution Explorer</li>
      <li styleclass="Normal">By choosing the context menu option &quot;Open&quot; on the Properties folder below the Project Icon in the Solution Explorer.</li>
    </list>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">All these options do the same and open the project properties dialog. This dialog has several pages.</para>
    <list id="3" type="ul" listtype="bullet" formatstring="&#183;" format-charset="SYMBOL_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="Normal"><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="PropPage-Application">Application</link></li>
      <li styleclass="Normal"><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="PropPage-Language">Language</link></li>
      <li styleclass="Normal"><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="PropPage-Dialect">Dialect</link></li>
      <li styleclass="Normal"><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="PropPage-Build">Build</link></li>
      <li styleclass="Normal"><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="PropPage-BuildEvents">Build Events</link></li>
      <li styleclass="Normal"><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="PropPage-Debug">Debug</link></li>
      <li styleclass="Normal"><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="PropPage-Resources">Resources</link></li>
      <li styleclass="Normal"><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="PropPage-Settings">Settings</link></li>
    </list>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">A description of each of these pages will follow in the next chapters.</para>
  </body>
</topic>
